- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with QBF (Quantified Boolean Formula) satisfiability problem, which is a topic within logic in computer science.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses mapping user specified functions to programmable logic.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of QBM tool for automated synthesis of hardware circuits.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the generation of test set formulas using a formal approach.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of a tool for automated synthesis of hardware circuits, which can be seen as a software engineering task.
